title: Modern Apartments with A/C and a plethora of natural light
posting_body: ['521 Stadium Place S, Seattle, WA 98104', 'The Wave takes modern design to new heights.', 'This 26 story apartment tower has an unparalleled look, location and breathtaking views (from up here you can see the 12th Person!).', 'The Wave is part of Stadium Place, a modern community designed so you can live, work and play in Seattle’s most famous neighborhoods.', 'The Wave luxury apartment homes offer floor to ceiling windows, top end finishes, quartz counters, air conditioning, walk in closets and wood flooring along with two roof top lounges with stunning views, a massive courtyard, high tech theater and a spa like fitness center.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Mobile Kitchen Island', 'Stainless-Steel Appliances', 'Air Conditioning', 'Washer and Dryer', 'High-End Finishes', 'Community Features:', 'Pet-Friendly Community with Two Dog Runs and a Paw Spa', 'Onsite Controlled Access Parking and Storage', 'Resident Lounge and Game Room', 'Private Resident Theater Room', 'Fitness Center and Yoga Room', 'Business and Conference Center', 'Expansive Rooftop Deck with Views of Mount Rainier, Puget Sound, and Downtown Seattle', 'Resident Package Lockers', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and Availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Contact us today for the most up to date information.']
